{"type": "article", "id": 13576, "title": "“星球大战”彩妆系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-17T07:55:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000241UjHcAxM2WpmeIlz1.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t“星战”年，彩妆也来凑热闹了。近日，美国彩妆品牌 CoverGirl 和 Star Wars 联手推出了一个彩妆系列，为即将上映的《星球大战7：原力觉醒》造势，目前推出的包括睫毛膏，唇彩，唇膏，指甲油等产品，全部采用黑色或银色包装，上面印有 Star Wars 标识，看起来酷酷的。至于这套彩妆效果如何，相信不久就能看到女星战粉丝发回评价了。产品将于 9 月正式全线推出。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141304Qo87YimvsLnJShyG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141305R8tdDBOvS7N2WiYp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141306V2lr98eOQ7uv4kdc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141306RfHvAKrIas1l7pFt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614130784TK3jVMQGbRDsaW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}